data.description: Beautifully updated home on corner lot with 24x24 detached SHOP which is fully insulated and has overhead door, wall AC and 220.  You will find newer paint inside and out, some newer flooring throughout and updated kitchen with stainless appliances.  The backyard has been made into an oasis with new grass and landscaping, new cement, an amazing patio with built in seating, bar, 2 grills, built in propane tank storage, and a projector with screen. A new gas line from meter to house was installed in 2020. The south side has a wonderful raised garden area. A Class 4 roof was added in 2017 and there is a sunroom that would make a great office! Don't let this one get by!
